{"tid":2292125,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"休班警遭「私了」　18 歲男認非法集結還押候判　地盤工脫傷人罪　襲擊罪成判罰款","createTime":"2020-11-19T09:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T10:51:23.000Z","uid":56115,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a3aac831aea8289c13dcd4413c234930e38b3ccd","tid":2292125,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"去年 9 月 25 日，網民在各區發起「遍地開花和你 shop」，期間一名休班警涉在屯門市廣場舉機拍攝在場市民，及後疑遭「私了」，32 歲地盤工人及 18 歲男生被控傷人罪及非法集結罪。裁判官今（18 日）在屯門裁判法院表示，事主記憶出錯，不少證供與案發影片不符，其中一被告更在案情所指圍毆發生前已離開，裁定傷人罪名不成立。但在圍毆發生前，兩人曾在扶手電梯打事主，故普通襲擊罪成。地盤工人被判罰款 3,000 元，非法集結罪則不成立；男生早前承認非法集結罪，裁判官明言「感化報告都唔適合」，為被告索取背景、勞教中心及教導所報告，押至下月 2 日判刑。"},{"pid":"2f7eab3ca9f2b14dc988cbaaa0d171fd2f97ce84","tid":2292125,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T09:06:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E9%81%AD-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-18-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%AA%8D%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4%E5%B7%A5%E8%84%AB%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA%E7%BD%AA-%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E5%88%A4%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%25AD-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-18-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2584%25AB%25E5%2582%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE%2F&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopakErG%2BwP2VMcW32eObqVUU%3D&h=572a41dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%258F%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%2581%25AD-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%2586-18-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E